    <tags>serv dsl microservices event-driven background-workers</tags>
    <summary>A Programming Language and complete microservices suite for background workers.</summary>
    <description>
Serv is a purpose-built compiled domain-specific language (DSL) that targets the orchestration of background tasks, message queues, and API gateways. 

### Features
* Compile-time safety for event brokers and databases.
* Integrated hot-reload.
* Native microservice topology visualization and request tracing.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/vyuvaraj/Serv-lang/blob/main/vscode-support/extension/changelog.md</releaseNotes>
